{"tid":1357094,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[所有人入嚟冷靜一下] 抗爭方程式","createTime":"2019-07-23T15:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T11:25:57.000Z","uid":190579,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"52012e5dcb751c5c10bc8781a5565ae15fafa3ac","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"運動行到今時今日唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有好幾次我地都走到去失敗邊緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但最終都捱過咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得有幾樣大原則好緊要，因為我地一直堅守，先至打到今日呢一步。歡迎討論，不喜請屌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>1) 和理不離不棄，同時勇武肯Be water ***(極重要) </ins></span><br />\n呢兩個缺一不可。<br />\n71為例，如果唔係和理不割蓆，照舊去立會支援勇武，勇武就不能無後顧之憂地攻入立會再全身而退<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果勇武唔肯Be water，守住退路既和理頂得幾耐? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>2) 不打第一槍</ins><br />\n每次我地都係先採取守態，食咗對家一拳先反擊，咁樣我地先出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3) 不用過份武力</ins><br />\n天琦講既係以武制暴，唔係以暴易暴。前者係話用合理武力制止暴力，後者係講用更強暴力復仇式攻擊。唔好曲解天琦，請尊重！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人屌狗都係屌佢地既過份暴力。政府一直就係等緊我地忍唔住，送一隻狗入浩園。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你在凝視深淵時，深淵也在凝視你。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>4) 夠聚焦</ins><br />\n受風向影響後一日內恢復理性討論，識破sidetrack。適度安排主線支線優次，雨露均霑，不影響主線下盡量兩邊都做。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">附送2個對家常犯錯誤，<span style=\"color: red;\">引以為戒</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">5) 不傷及無辜 ***(極重要) </span><br />\n政府警犬鄉黑不斷重覆既錯誤，極大程度上幫咗我地統一戰線。大家應該都明﹐唔多講<br />\n<br />\n6) 不因憤怒而失去理智<br />\n警犬不斷重覆既錯誤，佢地EQ低，小小事就私怨上腦發癲自爆﹐自暴醜態於鏡頭前，極大程度上幫咗我地文宣。同時令到上級命令同前線執行自相矛盾。71明明政府想打番輿論戰，但谷到狗狗緊哂火77發癲。713, 714 明明政府想打番輿論戰，送警犬入浩園，但警犬714自己都忍唔手，一家大細都兇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q: 呢個時候仲爭咩光環同民意?</strong><br />\nA: 出師有名唔係光環同民意咁簡單。運動去到今日今時，早已唔係單純既政治訴求，問題早已昇華至人道層面同價值層面。<br />\n一開始我地坐埋同一條船，只係因為我地有同一目標；但去到今日，我地坐埋同一條船，係因為我地有<span style=\"color: green;\">共同道德同價值觀。</span><br />\n我嚟問你，如果冇光環同民意，共同道德同價值，請問反送中人道基金邊有錢比義士打官司，記者仲會唔會如此不惜肉身企最前線，沙田仲會唔會天降物資，D街坊仲會唔會同我地一齊大力屌狗，各界仲會唔會咁堅定地不割蔗？<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>勇武為矛，和理為盾</strong></span>，拆掉勇武既盾，等同送勇武去死。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q: 點解不作為?</strong><br />\nA: 唔係不作為，只係要等對手開第一槍，我地再用<span style=\"color: green;\">合理武力</span>還擊。612如是, 71如是, 714如是, 721如是, 我希望726亦如昰<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q: 點解重要忍，點解唔可以先發制人。</strong><br />\nA: 我都好想呀屌，但請問<span style=\"color: red;\">你有冇槍，有冇坦克，有冇監獄</span>去制裁你既敵人? 如果答案係冇，我地就必須接受而家既<span style=\"color: red;\">政治現實</span>，我地絕對承受唔到一次硬碰硬正面衝突。每次我都好擔心勇武會比人一網打盡。跪求一齊嚟一齊走。"},{"pid":"6eeaa0527d0bb731df06f2a451d8edf5dcc988ea","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:58:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e462d5668b148528bcce2ff72890dcefa0c03d83","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:58:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0cf75706cb5afd465b198aff70fa4472b8e3bf2","tid":1357094,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"真理"},{"pid":"b152f3a634e105d19b429938cdfb559d579ef749","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d44f19eb13faf81dc782362fc08c4ffed79947b8","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75b429f5b840b3224c8b3713fbe9f517180b135","tid":1357094,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>集中5大訴求<br />\n1.撤回逃犯條例，永不重提<br />\n2.撤銷612暴動定性<br />\n3.撤銷示威者控罪並承諾永不追究<br />\n4.全面實行雙普選<br />\n5.成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任(包括警黑勾結元朗恐襲)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e499eaddfa74d35ea23dea6320cd2db9283c7e0c","tid":1357094,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384063ddd8e38852f28bf9e8d360e3f58d67c868","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:59:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b98f86e5515944c9d3b8318529fb729c5e8a4c82","tid":1357094,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:00:09.000Z","msg":"[7.21] 上環義士很可能已經死亡 <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dpgmeT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dpgmeT</a>"},{"pid":"109afa36f82ce71f72d91087d26958c88a771ffc","tid":1357094,"uid":271084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"推 真心推"},{"pid":"5195e22e5bffe5604a46bf6067ac23af90ff1c6a","tid":1357094,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:01:18.000Z","msg":"光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！"},{"pid":"cb1319cbd7a9945f5fb1be4d8f97490962aca33a","tid":1357094,"uid":267757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"警黑合作，無法無天。<br />\n不拆祠堂，只求公道。"},{"pid":"1d6bb6bfe645ede2dfc2fb5d58f68cec764926eb","tid":1357094,"uid":287397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c93d07050027b55899d2c6ac3780572a26524c1","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"448d3518770ec8ed27f7189f428b04cf9990c3f9","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:03:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4e0425d321194e295b62857de5944ae5e3aa36a","tid":1357094,"uid":285267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"好同意唔夠聚焦，轉哂風向批鬥黑警濫暴。每一次新行動訴求冇得到回應就俾其他事轉左焦點。最開始話堅持撒回依家都少左提，林鄭成功轉移視線。之前都有5大訴求，覺得係時候要再整理翻。"},{"pid":"cee339e3dfff6bead4fc0fcd744bb27cb0b14a7a","tid":1357094,"uid":276665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:05:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81d4e35bc8cb4f5a8870239d9d299771180c6378","tid":1357094,"uid":267240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"大力推"},{"pid":"f4a60ba5833fd02fc033d295e3e35a22de2ddfcb","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:06:54.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"1f8aa019c0f27ba1a3bc1fe02057f91b184f2407","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:08:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e5bedc448fead1d8b8368534ff091e88ba8216f","tid":1357094,"uid":270250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"輕輕幫推"},{"pid":"c717fc5ed663679247f211b19f16fe2d255ea0eb","tid":1357094,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d110123f32e7c8198cd82c2de1dc8a82d1cfb7bf","tid":1357094,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc179c9428d37d5f481e4906d15363622e95b03e","tid":1357094,"uid":287397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"大力推"},{"pid":"aa05f6cf415d9d14ec3b2782d1a0c23ea175c305","tid":1357094,"uid":267757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:12:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dae90f60d72e535f53b4c16105d4a06c60f8489","tid":1357094,"uid":269711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"１。全面撤回送中<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗暴動"},{"pid":"36500b309228b479f0de71d940c91f31b7e5d9bd","tid":